headline: This Artificial Intelligence (AI) Powerhouse Could Be Just Getting Started
summary: Artificial intelligence (AI) has long drawn the interest of investors.  The generative AI boom is a much more recent breakthrough, and it is driving considerable investment returns for companies like Nvidia and Palantir Technologies.  The stock that is well-positioned to start benefiting from the latest AI changes is Qualcomm (NASDAQ: QCOM).
